==== ENTRY 3 ====
HEADWORD: Rial
<hw>Ri"al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[From
<er>Royal</er>.]</ety> <def>A gold coin formerly current in England, of
the value of ten shillings sterling in the reign of Henry VI., and of
fifteen shillings in the reign of Elizabeth.</def> <altsp>[Spelt also
<asp>ryal</asp>.]</altsp> <rj><au>Brande & C.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

